Subject: [PATCH 21/34] netlink: add netlink handler for gfec (--show-fec)

Implement "ethtool --show-fec <dev>" subcommand showing Forward Error
Correction (FEC) settings using netlink interface command
ETHTOOL_MSG_PARAMS_GET with ETHTOOL_IM_PARAMS_FEC mask.

Signed-off-by: Michal Kubecek <mkubecek@suse.cz>
---
